<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />The words of Yahweh are pure words,</para>

<para style="q1">like silver purified in a furnace on the earth,</para>

<para style="q1">refined seven times.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />You are Yahweh! You keep them.</para>

<para style="q1">You preserve the godly people from this wicked generation and forever.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />The wicked walk on every side</para>

<para style="q1">when evil is exalted among the children of mankind.</para>
